                "invention-title": [
                    "Electricity-hydrogen co-production system and method for ultra-high temperature gas cooled reactor coupled mixed sulfur circulation",
                    "超高温气冷堆耦合混合硫循环的电氢联产系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an electricity-hydrogen co-production system and method for ultra-high temperature gas cooled reactor coupled mixed sulfur circulation. The system comprises an ultra-high temperature gas cooled reactor power generation unit; the system comprises a main loop of circulating inert gas composed of an ultra-high temperature gas cooled reactor and a power generation assembly; the inert gas serves as a heat source after absorbing heat in the ultra-high-temperature gas cooled reactor and enters the power generation assembly to expand to do work for power generation, and tail gas of the power generation assembly flows back to the ultra-high-temperature gas cooled reactor; the mixed sulfur circulating unit is in heat exchange connection with the ultrahigh-temperature gas cooled reactor power generation unit and comprises a sulfuric acid decomposer, an SO2 depolarization electrolytic tank and a sulfuric acid rectifying tower which form a hydrogen production loop for sulfuric acid circulation; the power generation assembly is electrically connected with the SO2 depolarization electrolytic tank and drives the SO2 depolarization electrolytic tank to generate hydrogen through electrolysis. Hydrogen, electric energy and high-temperature steam can be produced at the same time, heat, electricity and hydrogen poly-generation and comprehensive and effective utilization of energy are achieved, diversified energy requirements are met, and the energy utilization rate of the whole system is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请提出超高温气冷堆耦合混合硫循环的电氢联产系统及方法，系统包括超高温气冷堆发电单元；其包括超高温气冷堆和发电组件组成的循环惰性气体的主回路；惰性气体吸收超高温气冷堆中的热量后作为热源，并进入发电组件膨胀做功发电，发电组件的尾气回流至超高温气冷堆；混合硫循环单元与超高温气冷堆发电单元换热连接，包括硫酸分解器、SO2去极化电解池、硫酸精馏塔组成硫酸循环的制氢回路；发电组件与SO2去极化电解池电连接，驱动其电解产氢。本申请可以同时生产氢气、电能以及高温蒸汽，实现热电氢多联产和能量的综合有效利用，满足多样化的能源需求，提高系统整体的能源利用率。"
                }
            ]
